data.text: 66, of Honolulu, a retired Medical Technologist for Clinical Labs of Hawaii, passed away on February 29, 2020 at Straub Medical Center. He is survived by daughter, Marisa Sacks; daughter, Monchalee Ota and her husband, Kekoa; sister, Kathi Marciniak; and his beloved dog, Kahlua. He was preceded in death by his parents, Walter Steiger and Jeanne Mieko (Ishimoto) Steiger. Private services.
